{
  "texts": [
    "Miraculously, LLMs can natively perform textual tasks without even having been taught them.",
    "Given the rapid adoption of AI technologies, much attention has been paid to ChatGPT's practical and societal relevance.",
    "ChatGPT use has grown across a variety of application domains.",
    "ChatGPT has emerged as an undoubtedly popular tool in education (Michel-Villarreal et al., 2023).",
    "Indeed, the growing popularity of ChatGPT portends an important shift in the way that learners approach learning."
  ]
}